@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### ——— BHSA ———

### BHSA: Check status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bhsa/status

### BHSA: Load data (background task)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bhsa/load
Content-Type: application/json

### BHSA: Fetch passage (Ruth 1:1-6)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bhsa/passage?ref=Ruth%201:1-6

### BHSA: Fetch passage (single verse)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bhsa/passage?ref=Gen%201:1

### BHSA: Fetch passage (Psalm 23)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bhsa/passage?ref=Ps%2023:1-6
